1. *Noćne* tajne (Nominative, adjective) (Night secrets)
2. U toku *noćne* smene (Genitive, adjective) (During the night shift)
3. *Noćne* more (Accusative, adjective) (Night sea)
4. *Noćne* more (Locative, adjective) (At the night sea)
5. *Noćne* ptice su veoma glasne. (Nominative, noun) (Night birds are very loud.)
6. Kupila sam novu maskaru za *noćne* izlaske. (Genitive, adjective) (I bought a new mascara for night outings.)
7. Životinje su aktivne tokom *noćnih* sati. (Genitive, adjective) (Animals are active during night hours.)
8. Policija je zaustavila vozača u *noćnoj* vožnji. (Dative, adjective) (The police stopped the driver during the night drive.)
9. Ove godine organizujemo *noćnu* trku. (Accusative, adjective) (This year we're organizing a night race.)
10. Moja prijateljica radi kao medicinska sestra na *noćnoj* smeni. (Locative, adjective) (My friend works as a nurse on the night shift.)